{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"65cf6d3280c7f6b7a5f6c43632dc8e2f3952319f60daf29438dc44616d9d58ca","slug":"exercises.intro","location":"/exercises/intro.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"简介","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101","numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"source_url":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101/blob/main/source/exercises/intro.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101/edit/main/source/exercises/intro.md","thumbnail":"/seismology101/build/workflow-ef25449eba567526c61c33460e54ea4e.jpg","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"intro.md","url":"/seismology101/build/intro-2a4888157b1de21cd52b13ece8dc42ee.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"日常地震学科研工作中，使用地震学数据开展研究前，往往需要先获取观测资料，并做预处理和分析。\n经处理和分析得到的可靠数据可用于研究震源、地震学成像以及探索地球深部等。因此，这一部分将介绍\n日常地震学科研工作中的常用工作流程，主要以实际工作中会用到的代码为主。\n目的是帮助地震学新手快速熟悉地震学数据下载、处理以及分析的基础代码，然后直接可以开展实际科研工作。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"juSbEAcFes"}],"key":"ppKof44wO8"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震台站记录到的地震图会实时或隔一段时间后传输至数据中心（","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"eQPYAQl5x8"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Data Center","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"FvJQRqy0RD"}],"key":"Z2xip9AsCu"},{"type":"text","value":"），如\n","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"eQ09wOp4va"},{"type":"link","url":"https://www.iris.edu/hq/","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"EarthScope SAGE","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"ZjJ5QggdCL"}],"urlSource":"https://www.iris.edu/hq/","key":"R5Lh6uMHQ2"},{"type":"text","value":"（前身为 Incorporated Research Institutions for Seismology (IRIS)）。\n一般情况下，地震学科研工作者直接可以从数据中心下载到公开的波形数据（time series data）。\n此外，一些数据中心也会提供地震目录（catalog）和台站元数据（medadata）。","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"QcPjGK99ci"}],"key":"h11gy1KwtQ"},{"type":"container","kind":"figure","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/seismology101/build/workflow-ef25449eba567526c61c33460e54ea4e.jpg","alt":"\"地震学观测的获取和处理流程示意图。\"","width":"95%","align":"center","key":"d6ZMEsCogR","urlSource":"workflow.jpg"},{"type":"caption","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震学观测的获取和处理流程示意图。","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"key":"xjHUl2oVWk"}],"key":"OG8erv3uWh"}],"key":"uImxPszioA"}],"enumerator":"1","key":"pYCa8lKUQH"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以下是地震学数据实战常见流程：","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"OeLryv2gjC"}],"key":"tZOpN8mMpR"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"首先，我们可以通过 ","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"tp2tCko9si"},{"type":"link","url":"https://www.fdsn.org/webservices/","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FDSN Web Services","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"XdoBmOgmS5